    Interface Description
    DeterminateNewPoint
    This @FunctionalInterface is used in @Actions in order to determinate new point.

    Bounds
    This class specified the limits of the entities.
    UtilityMovement
    This class is used every time that you want move an entity and you have to do some controls.

    Actions
    This enum use the @FunctionalInterface @DeterminateNewPoint so, decide the future movement of the entity.

    MovementTypes
